<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Página de Seraph - posts</title><link href="https://ecrespo.github.io/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="https://ecrespo.github.io/feeds/posts.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>https://ecrespo.github.io/</id><updated>2012-12-14T09:00:00-05:30</updated><subtitle>Data Scientist </subtitle><entry><title>Separar código de pruebas de la documentación (doctest, 2da parte)</title><link href="https://ecrespo.github.io/separar-codigo-de-pruebas-de-la-documentacion-doctest-2da-parte.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2012-12-14T09:00:00-05:30</published><updated>2012-12-14T09:00:00-05:30</updated><author><name>Ernesto Crespo</name></author><id>tag:ecrespo.github.io,2012-12-14:/separar-codigo-de-pruebas-de-la-documentacion-doctest-2da-parte.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;En el &lt;a href="https://www.seraph.to/probar-codigo-con-doctest.html#probar-codigo-con-doctest"&gt;art&amp;iacute;culo anterior&lt;/a&gt; se explic&amp;oacute; como utilizar &lt;code&gt;doctest&lt;/code&gt; dentro de un c&amp;oacute;digo para realizar pruebas sobre la documentaci&amp;oacute;n de cada funci&amp;oacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ahora se explicar&amp;aacute; como realizar dichas pruebas de la documentaci&amp;oacute;n en un archivo aparte del c&amp;oacute;digo del programa. Se usar&amp;aacute; el mismo ejemplo del art&amp;iacute;culo anterior pero adaptandolo …&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;En el &lt;a href="https://www.seraph.to/probar-codigo-con-doctest.html#probar-codigo-con-doctest"&gt;art&amp;iacute;culo anterior&lt;/a&gt; se explic&amp;oacute; como utilizar &lt;code&gt;doctest&lt;/code&gt; dentro de un c&amp;oacute;digo para realizar pruebas sobre la documentaci&amp;oacute;n de cada funci&amp;oacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ahora se explicar&amp;aacute; como realizar dichas pruebas de la documentaci&amp;oacute;n en un archivo aparte del c&amp;oacute;digo del programa. Se usar&amp;aacute; el mismo ejemplo del art&amp;iacute;culo anterior pero adaptandolo a tener la documentaci&amp;oacute;n aparte en un archivo de texto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;El c&amp;oacute;digo se muestra a continuaci&amp;oacute;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ch"&gt;#!/usr/bin/env python&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="c1"&gt;# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="c1"&gt;#Se importa el m&amp;oacute;dulo math para calcular la raiz cuadrada.&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;math&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="c1"&gt;#Funci&amp;oacute;n raiz cuadrada.&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="c1"&gt;#Si a es mayor o igual a cero se calcula la raiz cuadrada&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

        &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;math&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sqrt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="c1"&gt;#Si es menor a cero se genera una excepci&amp;oacute;n donde se informa que a debe ser mayor o igual a cero.&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="k"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

        &lt;span class="k"&gt;raise&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ne"&gt;ValueError&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"a debe ser &amp;gt;= 0"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="vm"&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s1"&gt;'__main__'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="c1"&gt;#Se importa el m&amp;oacute;dulo doctest&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;doctest&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="c1"&gt;#Se realiza la prueba al archivo raizcuadra.txt&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;doctest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;testfile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"raizcuadrada.txt"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Como se ve se realiza la prueba al archivo raizcuadrada.txt. El archivo contiene lo siguiente:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Modulo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;raiz&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;cuadrada&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;=====================&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Usando&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="s1"&gt;'raizcuadrada'&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;------------------------------&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Primero&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;se&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;importa&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;la&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;funci&amp;oacute;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kn"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;raizcuadrada&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ejemplos de calculo de raiz cuadrada:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mf"&gt;3.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mf"&gt;5.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Traceback&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;most&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;recent&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;call&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;last&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="o"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="ne"&gt;ValueError&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;debe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ser&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ahora lo que viene es ejecutar el comando que devuelve el resultado de las pruebas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;python&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;doctest&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;v&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;raizcuadrada&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;txt&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Trying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="kn"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;raizcuadrada&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Expecting&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;nothing&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Trying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Expecting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Trying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Expecting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="mf"&gt;3.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Trying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Expecting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="mf"&gt;5.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Trying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Expecting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Trying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Raiz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;Expecting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Traceback&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;most&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;recent&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;call&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;last&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="o"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;

    &lt;span class="ne"&gt;ValueError&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;debe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ser&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;passed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;all&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;tests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

   &lt;span class="mi"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;tests&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;raizcuadrada&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;txt&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mi"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;tests&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="mi"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;passed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;failed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;


&lt;span class="n"&gt;Test&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;passed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Como se puede observar en este caso se realiza la importaci&amp;oacute;n del programa y luego se empieza las pruebas.&lt;/p&gt;
